snippet.title: Best VGM 1315 - 999 : Nine Hours, Nine Persons, Nine Doors - Morphogenetic Sorrow
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2222 - https://youtu.be/PFGusujntfI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
999 : Nine Hours, Nine Persons, Nine Doors (2010)
Morphogenetic Sorrow
Shinji Hosoe
